This attempts to hit the same sort of notes as SCP-348, but falls flat for a number of reasons. The first reason is that, unlike 348, this relies on incompetence and complete ignorance of the scientific process from the researcher involved to even arrive at this emotional situation. The second is that the ending, where a final gut punch really makes it work for a reader, is a reassignment note which only exists to promote an almost entirely unrelated article.







